                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">...and it would even fit in the concept of other spells in this level range, e.g. <ul><li>FoS/Fo7<li>Virtue/HoV<li>SoV/VQ<li>SoK/KM<li>Po9/Bo9<li>BoR/AoR</ul>
