                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If they make Tranq a single target version in its present form or that of VoQ they will have to reduce the mana cost to at least below 166m per cast. While it would be much easier to KEI the group than to single C4 them all you will still have lots of folks who want the superior buff. 
<br />

<br />
NOTE: This is all assuming the Enc does NOT have VoQ.
<br />

<br />
Not to mention, why wouldnt you want your group mates to have your best buffs you have to offer? Granted, rarely will you have a group full of casters that would make you cast this 6x but it does happen. 
<br />

<br />
In a raid environment however, this would absolutely rock. I am a raiding enc and have dreamed of the day when I can get my hands on the single target c5 hat from ldon raids but it is a long way off as my guild and I are still having fun plowing thru PoP. 
<br />

<br />
So while I do want an alternative to casting VoQ every time a single person dies it just doesnt seem feasible to get this way.
