                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Tranquility is 63, not 64.  I agree that Tranquility should be a single-target version of Voice of Quellious.  Nothing irritates me quite as much as having to cast VoQ every time we add someone to a group during a raid.  As already mentioned, click buffs don't work with /tgb on so Silken Augmenter's are inconvenient for raids.
